# aibc Project Rules

## Monorepo

- `packages/extension` — VS Code extension host (esbuild)
- `packages/webview` — IDE sidebar React UI (Vite)
- `packages/portal` — Web dashboard Earn + Advertise (Vite)
- `packages/api` — Backend API (Hono + SQLite dev)
- `packages/shared` — Shared TypeScript types

## Commands

```bash
npm install
npm run dev:api      # http://127.0.0.1:8787
npm run dev:portal   # http://127.0.0.1:5175
npm run build
npm run package
```

## API base

- Dev: `http://127.0.0.1:8787`
- Prod: `https://api.aibcmedia.com`
- Env: `AIBC_API_BASE`, `AIBC_DEV_BYPASS=1` for demo auth

## Privacy

Never collect source code, editor content, or clipboard data.
